  <td valign=3Dtop style=3D'padding:0in 5.75pt 0in 5.75pt'>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Weapon Preference: Fighter/Bombers and Torpedoes<o:p=
></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>A very hardy, relatively short amphibian species, th=
e <span
  class=3DSpellE>Tairoshan</span> developed on a home world that harbors fr=
equent
  large climate shifts because of its two large moons.<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span class=3DSpellE>Tairoshans</span> are not very
  intelligent but are extremely optimistic and na&iuml;ve creatures. Most l=
ife
  on Roshar evolved to support other life because of such adverse condition=
s,
  this has made <span class=3DSpellE>Tairoshans</span> extremely unequipped=
 to
  mix in the Galaxy because they judge everyone by their own standards, fin=
ding
  it extremely hard to imagine other races treating them badly despite past
  experience.<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Because of their nature they are a very likeable rac=
e and
  other races all love to trade with <span class=3DSpellE>Tairoshans</span>,
  often taking advantage of them.<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Extremely positive about their space program, <span
  class=3DSpellE>Tairoshans</span> believe meeting other life can only be a=
 good
  thing for them. All <span class=3DSpellE>Tairoshans</span> are enthusiast=
ic to
  spread out in the Galaxy.<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>On Roshan all life has a <span class=3DGramE>12 year=
</span>
  metamorphosis cycle because of one of the moons, this still happens
  throughout the Galaxy because each <span class=3DSpellE>Tairoshan's</span>
  cycle synchronizes with other <span class=3DSpellE>Tairoshans</span> arou=
nd
  them. Life goes in to a slowed down docile state while each individual
  changes sex and finds a new partner to reproduce.<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Tairoshans</span> use mecha=
nical,
  tentacle like robots for many jobs and have adapted this technology to
  quickly dock, refuel or load ships. The Rad Coupler allows for extremely
  efficient docking operations that can be achieved at high speeds.<o:p></o=
:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span class=3DSpellE>Tairoshans</span> usually stick
  together in large communities, able to easily colonize any <span class=3D=
GramE>water
  based</span> planets.</p>
